title: Mooncake Shop v1.05
description:
The very first and the only Mooncake Shop game available anywhere!

Set up your own mooncake bakery! Bake and make different kinds of mooncakes for the festivities.

From the classic white lotus mooncakes to the latest and unique snowskin mooncakes available in the market today.

Box it up for take out, combine it with exquisite tea like Pu 'er and Longjing tea and more!

Over 36 levels of fun and excitement managing your very own mooncake shop!

What's in this version:
Update:
Here's what is new in this update!
1.05 fix the score saving and levels being locked even after passing the level. Terribly sorry about this! This update should now fix this.
version 1.04 recommended update
Game is now working correctly for Nexus Tablets
Bug fixes and optimizations
version 1.04b hopefully will fix the crash on samsung galaxy devices.
Update now to prepare for the next major update. Otherwise your scores will be lost in the mext major update!
